^perangkat<n><regular><sg>$ ^anda<prn>$ ^dukung<v><av>$ ^kirim<v><process><sg>$ ^pesan<n><regular><sg>$ ^teks<n><regular><sg>$ ^yang<cnjsub>$ ^lebih<adj><av><trans><appl>$ ^batas<n><regular><sg>$ ^karakter<n><regular><sg>$ ^pesan<n><regular><sg>$

